case is the only one that needs runtime support (the 'tools:' block); Claude/Codex/Copilot use existing permission surfaces\",\"evidence\":\"iteration-003.md finding 3.7 + 3.8\"},{\"approach\":\"Treat A5 auto-surface as a single replacement problem\",\"reason\":\"Architecture-dependent: (a) loses it; (b)/(c) keep it. Migration cost for (a) is documentation + agent-prompt updates\",\"evidence\":\"iteration-003.md finding 3.6\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-06T09:05:00Z\",\"durationMs\":900000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-minimax-1780735927714-4462h3\",\"lineage\":\"minimax\"}\n","exit":0,"description":"Append iteration 3 JSONL record","truncated":false},"title":"Append iteration 3 JSONL record","time":{"start":1780737332727,"end":1780737332729}},"id":"prt_e9c373b87001GtBhwaanklXx2M","sessionID":"ses_163de1863ffeLd3K58IkmWaFwL","messageID":"msg_e9c3707420014kpm2t4sGmAJhp"}}
