ternal runtime dependency; either OpenCode ships it (1-3 weeks) or we ship a CLI shim (2-3 days). S3 is the migration critical path.\",\"evidence\":\"iteration-004.md finding 4.4 + 4.7\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-06T09:10:00Z\",\"durationMs\":900000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-minimax-1780735927714-4462h3\",\"lineage\":\"minimax\"}\n","exit":0,"description":"Append iteration 4 JSONL record","truncated":false},"title":"Append iteration 4 JSONL record","time":{"start":1780737671728,"end":1780737671730}},"id":"prt_e9c3c6084001DD6JWW2jRjE7De","sessionID":"ses_163de1863ffeLd3K58IkmWaFwL","messageID":"msg_e9c3c35740016Cx2OUb5sCyJCJ"}}
