chitecture comparison with go/no-go\",\n    \"status\": \"in_progress\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  },\n  {\n    \"content\": \"phase_synthesis: Generate research.md + final dashboard for the lane\",\n    \"status\": \"pending\",\n    \"priority\": \"high\"\n  }\n]","metadata":{"todos":[{"content":"phase_init: Initialize minimax lane state files (config, strategy, state.jsonl, registry, dashboard)","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop iteration 1: KQ1 - 37-tool parity matrix (KQ1)","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop iteration 2: KQ2 - Daemon-dependency audit","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop iteration 3: KQ3 - MCP-only affordances and replacements","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop iteration 4: KQ4 - Integration-surface migration","status":"completed","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_main_loop iteration 5: KQ5 - Architecture comparison with go/no-go","status":"in_progress","priority":"high"},{"content":"phase_synthesis: Generate research.md + final dashboard for the lane","status":"pending","priority":"high"}],"truncated":false},"title":"2 todos","time":{"start":1780737799029,"end":1780737799032}},"id":"prt_e9c3e606b0016iMJx68W22SxEY","sessionID":"ses_163de1863ffeLd3K58IkmWaFwL","messageID":"msg_e9c3e3cd4001pRSwWVOXcV6XNE"}}
