effort estimate (1 engineer, 12-16 days), and final go/no-go. Verdict: GO with architecture (c) — hybrid CLI that auto-spawns the daemon on demand.\",\"keyQuestions\":[\"kq5\"],\"answeredQuestions\":[\"kq5\"],\"ruledOut\":[{\"approach\":\"Single-binary CLI form\",\"reason\":\"Daemon is multi-process by design (Node parent + hf-model-server sidecar + SQLite daemon); CLI is one entry point, not one process\",\"evidence\":\"iteration-005.md finding 5.7; bin/mk-spec-memory-launcher.cjs:1-80 confirms multi-process\"},{\"approach\":\"Atomic migration\",\"reason\":\"Migration is composable per-tool and per-runtime; the S3 runtime config gate is the only true atomic step\",\"evidence\":\"iteration-005.md finding 5.8; 28 files / 125 refs split across 4 mechanical surfaces + 1 runtime gate\"}],\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-06T09:15:00Z\",\"durationMs\":900000,\"sessionId\":\"fanout-minimax-1780735927714-4462h3\",\"lineage\":\"minimax\"}\n===\nFinal state.jsonl line count:\n       7 /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/028-memory-mcp-cli-feasibility/research/lineages/minimax/deep-research-state.jsonl\n","exit":0,"description":"Append iteration 5 JSONL record and check state log","truncated":false},"title":"Append iteration 5 JSONL record and check state log","time":{"start":1780737934564,"end":1780737934566}},"id":"prt_e9c4065870015DF2Qess1Kf2wk","sessionID":"ses_163de1863ffeLd3K58IkmWaFwL","messageID":"msg_e9c40486e001o5FMT7SNpPatXE"}}
