dependency; S3 is the migration critical path\", \"iteration\": 4}\n+    {\"direction\": \"S2 as 'just search-and-replace'\", \"reason\": \"Inline tool calls in prompt bodies require CLI flag-syntax rewrite\", \"iteration\": 4},\n+    {\"direction\": \"S3 as 'just config edit'\", \"reason\": \"OpenCode 'tools:' block is the migration critical path\", \"iteration\": 4},\n+    {\"direction\": \"Single-binary CLI form\", \"reason\": \"Multi-process by design; CLI is one entry point, not one process\", \"iteration\": 5},\n+    {\"direction\": \"Atomic migration\", \"reason\": \"Composable per-tool and per-runtime; only S3 is truly atomic\", \"iteration\": 5},\n+    {\"direction\": \"(a) as the recommended architecture\", \"reason\": \"Operational cost (R1, R3, R5, R6) exceeds migration saving\", \"iteration\": 5}\n   ]\n }\n \n","additions":24,"deletions":19},"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/028-memory-mcp-cli-feasibility/research/lineages/minimax/findings-registry.json","time":{"start":1780738101470,"end":1780738101474}},"id":"prt_e9c4247100012GPCEMEqHkzuyG","sessionID":"ses_163de1863ffeLd3K58IkmWaFwL","messageID":"msg_e9c422ead0018OrDRe8l7DWErJ"}}
